data.description: Excellent location!!! Come see for yourself this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom Colonial located in Cortland. Two car garage w/gas heater. Step inside and enjoy the two-story foyer that leads into the eat-in kitchen where all appliances stay. The first floor boasts a formal dining room with hardwood floors, a large family room with a stone fireplace, a half bath, and a first-floor laundry room. Head upstairs to see three bedrooms, a full bath, and a spacious master bedroom with a large en suite complete with walk-in closet, shower, and jacuzzi tub.  Step outside and enjoy your private, wooded backyard from the composite deck. Walk across the bridge that spans the creek to your storage shed. ADT Security System included. New Sump pump in 2022. Call today to schedule your showing!
